Hoon Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hoon_Lee 0 Tong Hoon Lee (born 1973 in Plymouth, Massachusetts) is an American stage, film and television actor who played the role of Job on the Cinemax series Banshee and played the role of the King in The King and I on Broadway.
